<!-- 1 为何用 Hessian -->
<div class="panel">
  <svg width="100%" viewBox="0 0 680 310" role="img">
    <title>为何需要 Hessian 矩阵</title>
    <desc>权重之间存在相关性，量化一个权重的误差可以用其他权重补偿</desc>
    <defs><marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M2 1L8 5L2 9" fill="none" stroke="context-stroke" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></marker></defs>

    <!-- RTN 方式 -->
    <g class="c-red">
      <rect x="40" y="40" width="260" height="44" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="170" y="62" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">RTN：直接四舍五入每个权重</text>
    </g>
    <text class="ts" x="170" y="106" text-anchor="middle">每个权重独立处理，忽略相互影响</text>
    <text class="ts" x="170" y="126" text-anchor="middle">→ 误差在大模型上会累积</text>

    <!-- GPTQ 方式 -->
    <g class="c-teal">
      <rect x="380" y="40" width="260" height="44" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="510" y="62" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">GPTQ：量化后补偿其他权重</text>
    </g>
    <text class="ts" x="510" y="106" text-anchor="middle">量化 w₁ 产生误差 ε</text>
    <text class="ts" x="510" y="126" text-anchor="middle">→ 调整 w₂, w₃… 来抵消 ε</text>

    <!-- 分隔线 -->
    <line x1="340" y1="30" x2="340" y2="160" stroke="var(--color-border-tertiary)" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>

    <!-- 权重相关性说明 -->
    <rect x="40" y="170" width="598" height="100" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-border-secondary)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <text class="th" x="339" y="196" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">为何权重间可以互相补偿？</text>
    <text class="ts" x="339" y="218" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">输出 y = w₁x₁ + w₂x₂ + w₃x₃ + …（线性叠加）</text>
    <text class="ts" x="339" y="238" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">量化 w₁→ŵ₁，误差 δ₁ = ŵ₁ − w₁，只需让 δ₂x₂ = −δ₁x₁ 即可补偿</text>
    <text class="ts" x="339" y="258" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">补偿的最优量由 <tspan font-style="italic">H⁻¹</tspan>（Hessian 逆矩阵）决定</text>
  </svg>
  <div class="callout"><b>Hessian 的含义：</b>H = 2XX ᵀ 描述了各权重对输出误差的二阶贡献。H⁻¹ 的第 q 列告诉我们：量化 wq 后，每个其他权重应该被调整多少。</div>
</div>

<!-- 2 OBS推导 -->
<div class="panel">
  <svg width="100%" viewBox="0 0 680 340" role="img">
    <title>OBS框架推导：量化权重后如何补偿其余权重</title>
    <desc>OBS 是 GPTQ 的理论基础，通过约束优化推导出最优权重更新量</desc>
    <defs><marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M2 1L8 5L2 9" fill="none" stroke="context-stroke" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></marker></defs>

    <!-- 步骤框 -->
    <g class="c-purple">
      <rect x="40" y="30" width="600" height="46" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="340" y="53" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">优化问题：量化第 q 个权重，最小化其他权重的补偿误差</text>
    </g>

    <!-- 公式框1：目标函数 -->
    <rect x="40" y="100" width="288" height="90" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-border-secondary)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <text class="ts" x="184" y="124" text-anchor="middle">目标函数（泰勒展开到二阶）</text>
    <text class="ts" x="184" y="150" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)">min ½ δFᵀ HF δF</text>
    <text class="ts" x="184" y="170" text-anchor="middle">δF = 其余权重的调整量</text>

    <!-- 公式框2：约束 -->
    <rect x="352" y="100" width="288" height="90" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-border-secondary)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    <text class="ts" x="496" y="124" text-anchor="middle">等式约束（第 q 个权重已定）</text>
    <text class="ts" x="496" y="150" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)">eq ᵀ δF = quant(wq) − wq</text>
    <text class="ts" x="496" y="170" text-anchor="middle">即第 q 维的调整量固定为量化误差</text>

    <!-- 箭头 -->
    <line x1="340" y1="145" x2="340" y2="145" stroke="none"/>
    <line x1="200" y1="195" x2="340" y2="240" class="arr" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
    <line x1="496" y1="195" x2="380" y2="240" class="arr" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>

    <!-- 解析解 -->
    <g class="c-teal">
      <rect x="80" y="244" width="518" height="76" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="339" y="270" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">拉格朗日解：</text>
      <text class="ts" x="339" y="295" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)">δF = − (wq − quant(wq)) / [H⁻¹]qq × H⁻¹:,q</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <div class="callout"><b>解的含义：</b><code>[H⁻¹]qq</code> 是敏感度（越小 = 该权重越关键，越难量化）。<code>H⁻¹:,q</code> 是第 q 列，决定了误差如何"分配"到其余各权重。两者一除一乘，就完成了精确的误差补偿。</div>
</div>

