<!-- 4 算法全貌 -->
<div class="panel">
  <svg width="100%" viewBox="0 0 680 400" role="img">
    <title>GPTQ 完整算法流程</title>
    <desc>从输入校准数据到输出量化权重的完整步骤</desc>
    <defs><marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M2 1L8 5L2 9" fill="none" stroke="context-stroke" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></marker></defs>

    <!-- 步骤1 -->
    <g class="c-gray">
      <rect x="40" y="30" width="598" height="46" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="339" y="53" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">输入：W ∈ ℝ^(dout×din)，校准集激活 X ∈ ℝ^(din×N)</text>
    </g>

    <line x1="339" y1="78" x2="339" y2="106" class="arr" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>

    <!-- 步骤2 -->
    <g class="c-purple">
      <rect x="100" y="108" width="478" height="46" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="339" y="131" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">① 计算 H = 2XXᵀ，对 H 做 Cholesky 分解</text>
    </g>

    <line x1="339" y1="156" x2="339" y2="184" class="arr" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>

    <!-- 循环框 -->
    <rect x="40" y="186" width="598" height="158" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-border-secondary)" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="6 3"/>
    <text class="ts" x="60" y="204">for q = 0 → d_in (按列)</text>

    <g class="c-teal">
      <rect x="70" y="210" width="540" height="40" rx="6" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="340" y="230" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">② 量化：Q[:,q] = round( W[:,q] / scale ) × scale</text>
    </g>

    <g class="c-amber">
      <rect x="70" y="264" width="540" height="40" rx="6" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="340" y="284" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">③ 误差：E[:,q] = (W[:,q] − Q[:,q]) / [H⁻¹]qq</text>
    </g>

    <g class="c-coral">
      <rect x="70" y="318" width="540" height="20" rx="6" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="340" y="328" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">④ 补偿：W[:,q+1:] −= E[:,q] ⊗ H⁻¹[q, q+1:]</text>
    </g>

    <line x1="339" y1="348" x2="339" y2="366" class="arr" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>

    <!-- 输出 -->
    <g class="c-green">
      <rect x="100" y="368" width="478" height="24" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="339" y="380" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">输出：量化权重矩阵 Q，及每列的 scale / zero_point</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <div class="callout"><b>补偿的直觉：</b>步骤④是核心。量化第 q 列产生的误差向量 E，乘以 H⁻¹ 的对应行，精确地"预告"了这个误差会对后续各列的输出造成多少影响——然后立刻从 W 中减掉，让下一列量化时面对的是已经修正过的权重。</div>
</div>

<!-- 5 数值例子 -->
<div class="panel">
  <svg width="100%" viewBox="0 0 680 380" role="img">
    <title>GPTQ 简化数值示例：2×2 权重矩阵逐步量化过程</title>
    <desc>通过具体数字展示量化一个权重后如何补偿另一个权重</desc>
    <defs><marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse"><path d="M2 1L8 5L2 9" fill="none" stroke="context-stroke" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></marker></defs>

    <!-- 原始权重 -->
    <text class="ts" x="110" y="36" text-anchor="middle">原始权重 W</text>
    <g class="c-purple">
      <rect x="40" y="44" width="140" height="54" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="ts" x="110" y="68" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)">w₁ = 0.74</text>
      <text class="ts" x="110" y="87" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)">w₂ = 0.31</text>
    </g>

    <!-- H 矩阵 -->
    <text class="ts" x="310" y="36" text-anchor="middle">H⁻¹（示意值）</text>
    <g class="c-gray">
      <rect x="220" y="44" width="180" height="54" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="ts" x="310" y="68" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)">H⁻¹ = [[1.2, 0.4],</text>
      <text class="ts" x="310" y="87" text-anchor="middle" font-family="var(--font-mono)">        [0.4, 0.9]]</text>
    </g>

    <!-- 步骤说明 -->
    <text class="ts" x="560" y="36" text-anchor="middle">scale = 0.25（INT4）</text>
    <g class="c-amber">
      <rect x="440" y="44" width="200" height="54" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="ts" x="540" y="68" text-anchor="middle">scale = 0.25</text>
      <text class="ts" x="540" y="87" text-anchor="middle">round(x / 0.25) × 0.25</text>
    </g>

    <!-- 量化步骤 -->
    <line x1="110" y1="100" x2="110" y2="128" class="arr" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
    <g class="c-teal">
      <rect x="40" y="130" width="590" height="44" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="335" y="152" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">① 量化 w₁：round(0.74 / 0.25) × 0.25 = round(2.96) × 0.25 = 3 × 0.25 = 0.75</text>
    </g>

    <line x1="335" y1="176" x2="335" y2="204" class="arr" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
    <g class="c-coral">
      <rect x="40" y="206" width="590" height="44" rx="8" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <text class="th" x="335" y="228" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="central">② 误差：ε₁ = (0.75 − 0.74) / H⁻¹₁₁ = 0.01 / 1.2 = 0.00833</text>
    </g>

    <line x1="335" y1="252" x2="335" y2="280" class="arr" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
